---
// Who We Are - Storytelling Narrative
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-background">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">


    <!-- Narrative Flow -->
    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- The Beginning -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 bg-card/50 border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80">
            To anchor a global capital stack advancing SDG 6 and improve the lives of 1 billion people through resilient, 
            equitable access to clean water.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The Challenge -->
      <div class="py-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-card/50 border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <p class="text-foreground/80 text-sm">
              Water is becoming the world's most critical resource. As scarcity and contamination rise, so does the 
              urgency for bold, scalable solutions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-card/50 border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <p class="text-foreground/80 text-sm">
              In 2024, investor interest surged in technologies like desalination and advanced treatment - 
              solutions vital for environmental resilience and rich with market potential.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Our Approach -->
      <div class="bg-primary/5 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-6">Our Holistic Approach</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">1. Venture Building</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80">
              We identify the best water IP/ideas, build teams around them, and provide the capital and support needed to succeed.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">2. Strategic Investment</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80">
              Our VC Fund invests in promising water technologies and helps scale them through our global network.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">3. Industry Transformation</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80">
              Through our PE Fund, we acquire and transform existing water companies, driving innovation at scale.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="text-center pt-8">
        <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Join us in building a water-resilient future. Together, we can turn the tide on the global water crisis.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
          Get Involved
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
